{"id":"f44b6eeb-4c38-46ae-845e-59f6a14c4d7f","name":"John Grace [S]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(9, 9, 9);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(240, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Dating Time!</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">God sets you and John up on a date..</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Notice how there were buttons in the original? Moderation thought those were boobs. So I had to edit the image.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">[S] is an indicator of which version of John this is.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">S for Sinner.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">R for Reprieve.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Z for Zen.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Added a headcanon that they change color depending on the situation.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Also God got the entities in on the date thing.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dozer is the waiter for some reason.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kinda just pulled this out of my ass.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Mobrunrun/status/1969392350955745605\" target=\"_blank\">Art Creds</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"obLOHw-LVRhGZyh_P_ucG.webp","creator":"Pip_Peach","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🌈 Non-binary","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","⛪ Religion","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3062,"messages":40157,"created_at":"2025-09-21T22:19:51.393801+00:00"}